		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">统御械张嘴，在其前方生成水漩涡，牵引玩家，位于其内将持续造成<span color="#7fbfff">30%</span><span>伤害；3s后漩涡喷发，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">统御械瞄准玩家，标记并禁锢落点位置，随后发射一枚水球落在范围处，造成<span color="#7fbfff">85%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="442" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">构型械自身拥有<span color="#ffdfbf">180</span><span>点「应战对策」上限。角色进入「夜魂加持」状态时，会积攒</span><span color="#bfffbf">30</span><span>充能，维持时每秒积攒</span><span color="#bfffbf">10</span><span>充能，充满时进入「应战对策」模式：其将产生一不断追踪玩家的泉眼，并间歇喷出1-4次的水柱，持续造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">45%</span><span>伤害；「动量」越多，泉眼移速越快。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1392" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1393" y="650">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="399" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">统御械捏出一把水刀，进行左划、右划、纵合至多三段的攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,60%,75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">统御械进行俯冲，朝玩家方向袭来，接触造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害，至多重复3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="442" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">统御械立即移至场地中央，进入「荡除」状态，期间其身旁的2个水龙头将沿顺时针方向持续喷洒水流；<br/>当「动量」累积至7.4%/22.2%/44.4%时，其水柱将持续造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。喷水持续30s，与「急湍瀑泉」共享时间。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
