		<RichText x="9" y="1076" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">凝滞</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1248" width="435" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深渊抗性：战前<span color="#ffdfbf">380%</span><span>，开局</span><span color="#ffdfbf">280%</span><span>，荡除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">210%</span><span>，若期间</span><span color="#ffbfbf">未进入过「凝滞」或「夜魂」状态</span><span>，</span><span color="#dfdfdf">则</span><span>结束时全抗将升至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">80%</span><span>。<br/>液流动量：总量135，每0.4s积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1.481%</span><span>(2)，每次</span><span color="#bfffff">冰元素</span><span>攻击减少</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2.963%</span><span>(4)，初始自带</span><span color="#ffdfbf">23.7%</span><span>(32)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_31.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_32.png')" x="576" y="406" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_33.png')" x="576" y="662" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_34.png')" x="1248" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_35.png')" x="1248" y="406" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_36.png')" x="1248" y="662" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_37.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="1055" width="1002" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「<span textDecoration="underline">液流动量</span><span>」初始拥有一定值，随时间持续增长，受到</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>攻击后会回退；当动量积蓄至不同进度时，所产生的效果不同：<br/>当「动量」累积至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">&lt;7.4%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7.4%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">22.2%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">44.4%</span><span>/</span><span fontFamily="SDK_TW_Web" color="#ffdfbf">≥</span><span color="#ffdfbf">88.9%</span><span>时，统御械将：<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">减抗</span><span>并「凝滞」 / </span><span color="#ffbfbf">加抗</span><span>并开始喷水 / 水柱伤害提升至50% / 水柱伤害提升至100% / 额外多2枚水龙头，同时水龙头转速随着阶段进行不断增加；<br/>当进入「应战对策」的特殊攻击模式后，仍会累积「动量」，将其打空仍可进入「凝滞」；同样，在「动量」</span><span color="#ffdfbf">&lt;7.4%</span><span>时，不会进入「应战对策」状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_38.png')" x="720" y="970">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7统御械.assets/Image_39.png')" x="576" y="982" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
	</Group>
</Graphic>